\begin_layout Standard
Two important class attributes of a Container are:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\family typewriter
start
\family default
: a string of text containing the LyX command that we are about to process;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
and 
\family typewriter
ending
\family default
