\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Adding your own 
\family typewriter
Container
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
If you want to add your own 
\family typewriter
Container
\family default
 to the processing you do not need to modify all these files.
 You just need to create your own source file that includes the 
\family typewriter
Container
\family default
, the 
\family typewriter
Parser
\family default
 and the 
\family typewriter
output
\family default
.
 Once it is added to the 
\family typewriter
ContainerFactory
\family default
 eLyXer will happily start matching it against LyX commands as they are
 parsed.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The files 
\family typewriter
formula.py
\family default
 and 
\family typewriter
image.py
\family default
 have some examples of processing a command in just one file.
\end_layout

