FAQ
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
Q: I don't like how your tool outputs my document, what can I do?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
A: First make sure that you are using the proper CSS file, i.e.
 copy the existing 
\family typewriter
docs/lyx.css
\family default
